properties.DESCRIPTION:
25 Sept 2021
A year ago, in celebration of our 50th existence years on this earth, amidst covid, which saw our plan for an oversea trip went up in smoke, we decided perhaps a more meaningful way is to plant a tree in celebration of our friendship at AJC whose motto was non mihi solum, so meaningful. Hope it will inspires more to plant trees in our little red dot and bring shades and green to our future generation.
properties.Name: non mihi solum
